      "writtenOn": "2018-11-16T21:02:51Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "It should: it\u0027s a oneof from Binary, Text, and Datagram https://cs.chromium.org/chromium/infra/go/src/go.chromium.org/luci/logdog/api/logpb/log.proto?l\u003d177\u0026rcl\u003d233800ef69284400d5fc15827304c10cda6ef070\n\nI\u0027m not at all wedded to the idea of dumping *everything* in the content, rather than just the text. I put it like this at first so that if we find it\u0027s too much and not useful we can take it out later.",
      "parentUuid": "9ba39955_7fc0bdcc",
