        "id": 1001907
      },
      "writtenOn": "2018-11-16T00:42:59Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I\u0027m not sure this construction is necessary:\n\n   f :\u003d func(StreamChunkCallback, []*logpb.LogEntry) {\n     return func(*logpb.LogEntry) {\n        ... use buf ...\n     }\n   }\n   return f(cb, []*logpb.LogEntry{})\n\nvs.\n\n   var buf []*logpb.LogEntry{}    // note that a nil slice here is fine\n   return func(*logpb.LogEntry) {\n     ... use buf ...\n   }",
      "revId": "1847cdcf2e649bbc021ec35b5643f3a50cac041a",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
      "unresolved": true
