        "id": 1134874
      },
      "writtenOn": "2018-11-16T21:02:51Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I\u0027ve swapped for\n\nvar buf []*logpb.LogEntry\nbuf \u003d nil\n\nsince the construction in the second excerpt fails with\n\nclient/butler/bundler/datagramParser.go:170:27: syntax error: unexpected { at end of statement\nclient/butler/bundler/datagramParser.go:171:2: syntax error: non-declaration statement outside function body",
      "parentUuid": "c1640158_92b7608c",
      "revId": "1847cdcf2e649bbc021ec35b5643f3a50cac041a",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
