      "writtenOn": "2018-11-16T21:02:51Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Yep.\n\nTrue. Actually, if le is not partial, then buf *should* be empty because the previous complete log should have gone through, unless something went wrong and we dropped a LogEntry (which is not supposed to happen due to when this is called), right?\n\nI don\u0027t like the idea of assuming buf is empty. What do you think of panicking if it isn\u0027t?",
      "parentUuid": "a8b98f7f_adfa817f",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 173,
        "startChar": 3,
