      "message": "allocate the slice with the correct capacity:\n\n   dgSize :\u003d 0\n   for _, lePart :\u003d range buf {\n     dgSize +\u003d len(lePart.Data)\n   }\n   bytes :\u003d make([]byte, 0, dgSize)\n   for _, lePart :\u003d range buf {\n     part :\u003d assertGetDatagram(lePart)\n     bytes \u003d append(bytes, part.Data...)  # doesn\u0027t cause allocation now\n   }",
      "range": {
